            -119.271183,43.876489,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>ZX Pond</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/umsh/AN6v0v65rMmVhqAQuOBqNRpBRTuwNaN7m199QmFGSJtgRNJQtMKvJH65CTFhDOTMJhlS_tJyk2es3lwZhbmNQwlWXX_GyDYLqrJ-rjan8p75LMkzIesOLwQoYYuM21FMvTJrtGWYVui19V6KAYYrQSa-IBY" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>This small pond is for kids under 14 and seniors over 65.  The pond is located on private property, but access is allowed for fishing.  The pond is stocked four times a year with rainbow trout.  Most of the fish are harvested within three weeks of stocking.<br> <br>Fish species: rainbow trout<br><br> <br>ODFW Recreation Report (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/RR/southeast/)<br><br><br><br>Trout Stocking Schedule (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/trout_stocking_schedules/)<br>Fishing Regulations (http://www.dfw.state.or.us/resources/fishing/reg_changes/index.asp)]]></description>
